OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,FEmergency departments are trialling a
OL,7,Fnew rapid blood test - which will help
OL,8,Fdiagnose life-threatening conditions
OL,9,Fin children such as sepsis or
OL,10,Fmeningitis.
OL,12,FThe 15-minute test is able to
OL,13,Fdistinguish between bacterial and
OL,14,Fviral infections fast-tracking
OL,15,Fdiagnosis, with many doctors claiming
OL,16,Fthey have already seen the benefits
OL,17,Ffor patients.
