OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,FIt means medics will no longer have to
OL,7,Fwait hours for the results of blood
OL,8,Ftests, and could instead deliver
OL,9,Fimmediate antibiotics if needed.
OL,11,FThe trial, funded by NHS England, is
OL,12,Fbeing rolled out at Alder Hey
OL,13,FChildren's Hospital in Liverpool, as
OL,14,Fwell as St Mary's Hospital in London
OL,15,Fand Great North Children's Hospital in
OL,16,FNewcastle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
