OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,FIn one case, a child with
OL,7,Fmeningococcal meningitis was treated
OL,8,Fmuch more quickly and another with
OL,9,Fsepsis started antibiotics straight
OL,10,Faway.
OL,12,F"Many of the children who come to
OL,13,Fhospital have a fever and this test
OL,14,Fcan quickly distinguish between a
OL,15,Fminor viral illness like a cold, or a
OL,16,Fmore serious infection," says Enitan
OL,17,FCarrol, professor of paediatric
OL,18,Finfection at the University of
OL,19,FLiverpool.
