OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,F"Our study is investigating whether
OL,7,Fthis definitive test for a bacterial
OL,8,For viral infection will be useful in
OL,9,Fhelping doctors make faster decisions
OL,10,Fand reducing the use of unnecessary
OL,11,Fantibiotics ` all of which is better
OL,12,Ffor patients and the NHS."
OL,14,FDr Charlotte Durand, consultant in
OL,15,Fpaediatric emergency medicine at Alder
OL,16,FHey also added that the test "could
OL,17,Fhave a massive impact on the emergency
OL,18,Fcare of paediatric patients".
