OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,FMeMed BV claims it is "the first FDA-
OL,7,Fcleared host-immune response assay for
OL,8,Faccurately distinguishing between
OL,9,Fbacterial and viral infections in just
OL,10,F15 minutes and turns complex immune
OL,11,Fsignals into one clear result powered
OL,12,Fby machine learning."
OL,14,FThe study looking at the test will run
OL,15,Funtil March and could help doctors
OL,16,Fmake faster decisions, and reduce the
OL,17,Fneed for unnecessary antibiotics.
OL,26,@nD@WOUtD@UO]
