OL,3,CRapid blood test for children 'could
OL,4,Cspot sepsis and save lives'
OL,6,F"Making the right decision around
OL,7,Fearly antimicrobial prescribing in
OL,8,Fchildren who need antibiotics the most
OL,9,Fhas the potential to save dozens of
OL,10,Fyoung lives every year," Dr Ron
OL,11,FDaniels, founder and chief medical
OL,12,Fofficer of the UK Sepsis Trust.
OL,14,F"Using antibiotics more wisely `
OL,15,Fmeaning both withholding them in
OL,16,Fpeople who won't benefit and giving
OL,17,Fthem urgently to people who need the
OL,18,Fmost ` has never been more important."
